Dear all,

Bioconductor is switching from Slack to Zulip as our main community chat platform on Monday 2 June 2025.

This change will preserve message history and support more structured, open discussions. Zulip offers topic-based threads, full history access, and better support for distributed collaboration ? all aligned with our open-source mission.

Timeline:

  *   30 May ? Final Slack export
  *   1 June ? Slack Pro ends
  *   2 June ? Zulip goes live (Slack channels renamed and set to read-only)

Details and background:
https://blog.bioconductor.org/posts/2025-05-29-slack-to-zulip/

Existing Slack users will receive an invite by email. Others can join from 2 June:
https://community-bioc.zulipchat.com

For help during the transition, see the blog post above.

Best,
